data.title: DaVinci Ruby Recliner and Glider
data.description: Lull your baby to sleep with the warmth of your arms and the gentle motions of the DaVinci Ruby Recliner and Glider. This chair is upholstered in plush polyester fabric, smoothly glides forwards and backwards, and can swivel a full 360 degrees.

data.title: DaVinci Olive Upholstered Swivel Glider with Ottoman
data.description: The DaVinci Olive Glider with Ottoman has been thoughtfully designed to meet mom's and baby's feeding time needs then transition to your home in the later years.

data.title: DaVinci Piper All-Purpose Upholstered Glider Recliner
data.description: We worked with moms to design the DaVinci Piper Glider Recliner so that it has exactly the features you need. The 360 swivel motion, forward and backward gliding function and plush popup leg rest provide comfort for feeding and putting baby to rest.

data.title: Capresso Infinity Die Cast Conical Burr Grinder
Introducing the Vitamix Explorian Series E310
data.description: Discover true high-performance blending with the E310. Featuring standard controls and our iconic blending power, the E310 quickly and easily creates steaming-hot soup, delicious smoothies, and so much more.

data.title: Introducing the Vitamix Explorian Series E320.mp4
data.description: Explore how easy it is to make healthy, whole-food recipes at home. From appetizers to dessert, the 64-ounce container is ideal for blending medium to large batches for family meals or entertaining.

data.title: How To Make Snowball Cookies
data.description:
Learn how to make cookie dough in your Vitamix. 

Powdered sugar coats these light and airy cookies, which are just as fun to form as real snowballs

data.title: City Mini GT by Baby Jogger
data.description: Taking the City Mini to the next level, the City Mini GT gives you the ability to pave your own way. All-terrain wheels let you decide how far you want to go off the beaten path. And with little touches like an adjustable handlebar to adapt to the parent's height, and a hand-operated parking brake, the City Mini GT is very accommodating.

data.title: Introducing the NutriBullet Pro - 900 Series
data.description:
We are thrilled to introduce a new member to the NutriBullet family.  The NutriBullet 900 boasts a more powerful motor with 25,000 RPMs, new accessories and a Blast with an even smoother finish.  You are going to love this product.  Check out our video to see all the latest updates!
